# Known regressions

When editing code in this repo (especially frontend, mobile app, or areas mentioned in AGENTS.md):

1. Read the project root file **AGENTS.md**.
2. Check the **"Known regressions and fixes"** section.
3. If your changes touch an area that has a documented regression, follow the fix or pattern described there so the same issue is not reintroduced.
